T02TD3705E:4b-36: 'phan ni mchod pa'i lha mo la //
T02TD3705E:4b-37: dril bu stong pa nyid kyi sgra //
T02TD3705E:4b-38: zla tshes thabs dang shes rab yin //
T02TD3705E:4b-39: tog ni mi nub rgyal mtshan no //
T02TD3705E:4b-40: logs rgyan phyam mgo 'dzi pa tri //
T02TD3705E:4b-41: kha nas rin chen phreng ba ni //
T02TD3705E:4b-42: dra ba dra ba phyed gyur pa //
T02TD3705E:4b-43: dbyibs dang ye shes brda yin no //
T02TD3705E:4b-44: sgo rgyan rnam pa mang yod kyang //
T02TD3705E:4b-45: re zhig dbang gi rtags bcu dang //
T02TD3705E:4b-46: rgyan dgu dang ni rdzas brgyad dang //
T02TD3705E:4b-47: rin chen bdun dang brda drug go //
T02TD3705E:4b-48: bzlog ste brda drug bshad pa las //
T02TD3705E:4b-49: steng gi chos kyi 'khor lo ni //
T02TD3705E:4b-50: gtso bo'i rtags te ri dags ni //
T02TD3705E:4b-51: 'khor gyi brdar ni shes par bya //
T02TD3705E:5a-2: nges don sgra ste gand'i ni //
T02TD3705E:5a-3: drang don sgra zhes gsungs pa'o //
T02TD3705E:5a-4: thabs dang shes rab mtshon pa ni //
T02TD3705E:5a-5: rdo rje dril bu gnyis yin no //
T02TD3705E:5a-6: rin chen bdun ni 'di yin te //
T02TD3705E:5a-7: dbang gi 'khor lo rin chen dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-8: lha mo btsun mo rin chen dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-9: sgo ba dmag dpon tshul dgu dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-10: mngon shes blon po bya ba ste //
T02TD3705E:5a-11: stobs bcu glang po rin po che //
T02TD3705E:5a-12: rdzu 'phrul ri dags rta yi tshul //
T02TD3705E:5a-13: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen no //
T02TD3705E:5a-14: rdzas brgyad bdud 'joms rgyal mtshan dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-15: thugs rje'i gdugs dang dpal be'u'i thugs //
T02TD3705E:5a-16: bdud rtsi'i bum pa mi snyems nya //
T02TD3705E:5a-17: chos kyi dung dang dgos 'dod skong //
T02TD3705E:5a-18: chos kyi 'khor lo de ltar ro //
T02TD3705E:5a-19: sgo khang nang gi rgyan dgu ni //
T02TD3705E:5a-20: smad na nyon mongs zil gyis gnon //
T02TD3705E:5a-21: glang dang seng ge ngang pa dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-22: stobs dang mi 'jigs tshad med de //
T02TD3705E:5a-23: s'a la'i shing gi tshal yin no //
T02TD3705E:5a-24: bar na lam rnams so sor 'byed //
T02TD3705E:5a-25: ri dang mi dang srang khram dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-26: g-yo dang 'byed dang bstab pa ste //
T02TD3705E:5a-27: blon po rin po che bzhin no //
T02TD3705E:5a-28: steng na sdug bsngal dang du len //
T02TD3705E:5a-29: klu dang chu srin ga ru da //
T02TD3705E:5a-30: ye shes thugs rje'i byin rlabs te //
T02TD3705E:5a-31: khyung gis klu rgyal bslang ba bzhin //
T02TD3705E:5a-32: dbang gi rtags bcu 'di lta ste //
T02TD3705E:5a-33: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang ;
T02TD3705E:5a-34: / go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-35: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-36: snying po lnga yis ye shes dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-37: chos mos rdzu 'phrul smon lam dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-38: skye las tshe dang longs spyod dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-39: sems la dbang ba go rims so //
T02TD3705E:5a-40: gdan gyi don rtags mi 'jigs stobs //
T02TD3705E:5a-41: rdzu 'phrul dbang dang las kyi khri //
T02TD3705E:5a-42: thabs dang shes rab skyon med dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-44: brten pa lha yi don rtags ni //
T02TD3705E:5a-45: lha dang lha mor bstan pa yang //
T02TD3705E:5a-46: gzhi ni gzhung dang 'dzin pa ste //
T02TD3705E:5a-47: lam ni thabs dang shes rab yin //
T02TD3705E:5a-48: 'bras bu dbyings dang ye shes so //
T02TD3705E:5a-49: sku dang sku mdog phyag rgya dang ;
T02TD3705E:5a-50: / phyag mtshan bzhugs stabs tshul dang ni //
T02TD3705E:5a-51: rgyan chas don gyi rnam grangs ni //
T02TD3705E:5a-52: grub pa rtags kyi phyag rgya dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-53: mtshon pa thabs kyi phyag rgya dang //
T02TD3705E:5a-54: mdzad pa las kyi phyag rgyar sbyar //
T02TD3705E:5a-55: de yang rgyud rgyal ma lus kyi //
T02TD3705E:5a-56: dgongs pa mdor ni bsdus pa yin //
T02TD3705E:5b-0: mtshan dang dpe byad 'od dang @5b gsum //
T02TD3705E:5b-1: bsod nams rdzogs shing yon tan mtshon //
T02TD3705E:5b-2: sems can don rnams mdzad pa ste //
T02TD3705E:5b-3: rgyas par mdo sde'i dgongs pa bzhin //
T02TD3705E:5b-4: don rtags rtags kyi chos mthun ni //
T02TD3705E:5b-6: gzhan du chos mthun mtha' yas pa //
T02TD3705E:5b-7: rgyud dang rtog pa rnams las byung ;
T02TD3705E:5b-8: / dkyil 'khor dbang dang dam tshig gsum //
T02TD3705E:5b-9: rgyud rnams kun gyi srog shing pas //
T02TD3705E:5b-10: rnal 'byor gsang sgor zhugs rnams kyis //
T02TD3705E:5b-11: gces spras yid kyi gzhung 'di spyad //
T02TD3705E:5b-12: dkyil 'khor don bsdus rgyud kyi man ngag 'di //
T02TD3705E:5b-13: nongs su nges kyis lha la bzod par gsol //
T02TD3705E:5b-14: 'di brtsams dge bas sems can ma lus kun //
T02TD3705E:5b-15: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi klong du gnas gyur cig / slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa /
T02TD3705E:5b-16: dkyil 'khor gyi chos mdor bsdus pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3705E:5b-18: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po sangs rgyas gsang bas /
T02TD3705E:5b-20: bran ka mu ti ta gnyis la brdzangs pa /
T02TD3705E:5b-21: bod yul du lo ts'a ba ka ba dpal brtsegs la sogs pas bsgyur ba'o//
